{"tid":2285964,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"西環男子凌晨墮樓亡 居民事隔半日始發現","createTime":"2020-11-14T14:22:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T15:46:00.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"52ac4b5fbf591fea7a9399507c74f0a216747366","tid":2285964,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T14:22:19.000Z","msg":"下午3時許，西環均益大廈二期有住戶報案，指一名男子倒卧天井。警員接報到場，證實男子25歲姓羅，已告不治。警方於現場沒有撿獲遺書，初步相信他從上址天台墮下，死因有待驗屍後確定。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，住戶早在今日凌晨已聽到巨響，曾出門查看但無發現，延至今日下午才發現遺體。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201114/NNY6VARZKFA33E6ZTMP27Q2B2M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201114%2FNNY6VARZKFA33E6ZTMP27Q2B2M%2F&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNyzvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=d436bcad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201114%2FNNY6VARZKFA33E6ZTMP27Q2B2M%2F&h=d6c55dee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201114/NNY6VARZKFA33E6ZTMP27Q2B2M/</a>"},{"pid":"cf9c5798333c29b3b9734f1785914ba8bc14e71f","tid":2285964,"uid":362346,"like":6,"dislike":13,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T14:23:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一年了 都仲有人比人掉落街"},{"pid":"2e6668de1f8712eada3961f78adc662754d56db3","tid":2285964,"uid":290118,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cf9c5798333c29b3b9734f1785914ba8bc14e71f","tid":2285964,"uid":362346,"like":6,"dislike":13,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T14:23:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一年了 都仲有人比人掉落街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T14:25:02.000Z","msg":"同志聰明咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wai